com.nineoldandroids.view.animation

类 AnimatorProxy

  • java.lang.Object
    • android.view.animation.Animation
      • com.nineoldandroids.view.animation.AnimatorProxy
  • 所有已实现的接口:
    Cloneable

    public final class AnimatorProxy
extends android.view.animation.Animation
    A proxy class to allow for modifying post-3.0 view properties on all pre-3.0 platforms. DO NOT wrap your views with this class if you are using ObjectAnimator as it will handle that itself.

    • 嵌套类概要
